        type - the type of the process.
        creationDate - the date when the process was created.
        lastModifiedDate - the last date when the process was modified.

        status - the status of the process.
        frequence - the frequence of the process.
        startingTime - the time when the process started.
        lastRunTime - the time when the process run for the last time.
        runNumber - the number of run of the process.
        processingBlocks - the processing block.
        logUrl - the URL where the log of the process is stored.
